title: SynthWave Music Pack 10
description: 10 original track and several seamless loopable versions.
longDescription:
SynthWave Music Pack 10 includes 10 original tracks inspired by the sounds of analog synthesizers and the general vibe of cyberpunk and sci-fi. Also contains several seamless loopable versions.
